00:34:52.842 --> 00:34:56.954
We added some text above it that says, "Get personalized recommendations,"

00:34:57.040 --> 00:35:01.077
so you know what you're going to find
if you click that link.

00:35:02.710 --> 00:35:03.710
Finally,

00:35:04.255 --> 00:35:06.646
perhaps the largest change was

00:35:06.771 --> 00:35:09.116
when you are on the all offerings page,

00:35:09.662 --> 00:35:12.966
the topic selection
is a series of radio buttons.

00:35:13.260 --> 00:35:15.991
We had styled them
to look like radio buttons,

00:35:16.093 --> 00:35:19.541
and they interacted with them
just like radio buttons.

00:35:20.475 --> 00:35:21.525
The way it worked was

00:35:21.596 --> 00:35:24.122
you would change the radio button
to another option,

00:35:24.190 --> 00:35:29.642
and you would hear in a screen reader
something like 13 offerings below.

00:35:30.104 --> 00:35:31.454
Then you would have to move

00:35:31.573 --> 00:35:34.229
