a little more like regular buttons.

00:35:54.113 --> 00:36:00.527
They look like separate clickable objects,
not a form field with one setting.

00:36:01.081 --> 00:36:05.556
Also, you can individually focus
on each one of these like a regular button

00:36:05.595 --> 00:36:07.985
and hit enter or space bar
on the keyboard.

00:36:08.332 --> 00:36:10.662
When you do that,
you make that selection,

00:36:10.733 --> 00:36:14.940
it will slide you down and move focus
to the start of the results list.

00:36:15.059 --> 00:36:18.000
It skips over
all the intermediate content,

00:36:18.188 --> 00:36:22.492
takes you right to the information
that you had just made a selection to see.

00:36:24.610 --> 00:36:28.110
Those were some of the things we did
and some of the things we learned.

