00:39:13.145 --> 00:39:14.145
on their visit.

00:39:14.966 --> 00:39:18.736
Also, make sure that
every design and content detail works

00:39:18.783 --> 00:39:20.163
to ease the experience.

00:39:20.537 --> 00:39:23.332
Small things
that web designers take for granted,

00:39:23.417 --> 00:39:28.647
like icons and staggered layouts
